>\n為自由抗爭 制度已失衡<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">Fight for freedom, no faith in the systems</span> </strong>"},{"pid":"085c8a0defa18eea301834012303ce2380c716ba","tid":1551474,"uid":74929,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T04:31:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/W16DxAR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FW16DxAR.jpg&h=6b663e35&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/B1mTkZ7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FB1mTkZ7.jpg&h=106f1e65&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/09/08/121821_334341e1fd8cd0795176f952631cddf0.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F09%2F08%2F121821_334341e1fd8cd0795176f952631cddf0.jpeg&h=0ace8822&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0Gvdmuh.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0Gvdmuh.jpg&h=88cf1465&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><ins>美國國歌唔同大陸國歌唔需要一定跟著唱 大部份場合只有一個領唱者</ins> <br />\n<br />\n唔識唱嘅話單手放心口就得<br />\n唔想放喺心口嘅話面向國旗都可<br />\n<br />\n記得除帽 口罩要帶保護返自己<br />\n美國佬好隨和其實着咩都冇所謂<br />\n<ins>最緊要有人到有心最重要</ins></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>今日大家美國領事館見</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n緊急9月8號 weconnect美國重要日子 注意事項<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1551454\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1551454</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"a3cbd15b297ed1781cab2788aae311e8591d7c0c","tid":1551474,"uid":66798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T04:31:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c50